data.description:
Renovated detached house on 1 acre with a fence and newly addition detached cabin office. House has 2 bedrooms, 1 bath, HVAC central air/heat serviced regularly, nice bathroom with ceramic tile, hard wood floors in front room and hallway, carpet in bedrooms, has attic & basement, & security camera. 

And backyard detached cabin has ceramic tile, sheet rock, a/c, heater, refrigerator, office desk, portable sink/toilet and is a cozy space that is 24FT X 12Ft.

$230k includes cabin office. If you don't want the cabin office price can be lowered. *View in person by appointment only* Closing: LUEDER, LARKIN & HUNTER, LLC 3800 Camp Creek Parkway. Agent is Rick CDE.

No solicitations, & not for rent & no low balls. Thank-you.
data.whatILove: Stand alone privacy, large yard, fence, hardwood floors, and newly added backyard detached cabin office.
